	   <tr><td colspan=2>Shield skin takes a max of 55pts of damage, that is it.&nbsp;&nbsp;It is a level 19 spell and as for its uses on a tank, you are right it is crap, but for us wizards who spend our time trying not to get hit it isn't a bad little buffer before we start taking actual damage, hell I still use it at 54, and it hasn't failed me yet, well except when I snare or nuke myself, hehe.  Hope this helps friend.<br>&nbsp;<br>Brodiciusx<br>54 Wizard<br>Tunare's Aberration<br>Tunare</td></tr>
