	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f105584529697062><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=11&mid=105584529697062>RE: What is Kei?</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=11&mid=105584529697062#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=179491><span id=Scholar>Archibald</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>25 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Jun 17th 7:03 AM 2003</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.37]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Emajica,<br><br>KEI stands for Koadic's Endless Intellect. KEI is a level 60 Enchanter spell. It has the following effects:<br>1: Increase Mana Pool by 250<br>2: Increase Mana by 14 per tick<br>3: Increase INT by 25<br>4: Increase WIS by 25<br>It lasts for at least 2.5 hours. It can only be cast on you when you are grouped with the person casting it, and you must be of level 46 or over for it to stick on you - this level requirement is the result of a recent patch (before you could be of any level and it would stick).<br><br>Hope that answers all your questions. Of course any sort of caster loves this buff!!<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
