	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well I know in Norrath it is a land of getting xp quick and good loot, but I thought I would throw this out anyways.&nbsp;&nbsp;Around level 51 or so go out to Erud's crossing and be ready for some fishing.  There are killer sharks in the water, granted they are dark blue and some tough bastages, but I had fun going in the water as bait, getting them to aggro and then root nuking them to death. Was challenging, because they come in two's usually, but the reward is getting some xp still, and the fact that they drop gems/jewelry that average about 80pp at the vender right there on the island, about 1 in 3 seemed to drop something decent, and while you are medding you can pull out your favorite pole and throw in a line.  Well if you try this good luck.  <br>&nbsp;<br>Brodiciusx<br>54 Wizard<br>Tunare's Aberration<br>Tunare</td></tr>
