	   <tr><td colspan=2>As soon as you get your lvl 34 spells go to Dawnshroud peaks. Go Invis and run to the entrance to GE, pull Tribals up to the steps. Its good to have a healing partner(I grouped with a Shaman friend of mine) and its great exp. These tribal things are casters but there not very good, and very easy to kill for the exp they give. You can also get a full group going, If its well balanced you can have the puller get 8 of those things at a time. The Tribals also have good loot they drop bricks of acrilyia and weapons that you can sell to the newbies in the bazaar, all and all a great place. Note be very carefull of trains in this zone they happen all the time, if you see a group of rockhppers Gate without hesitation, DO NOT try to zone into GE its very ugly. If there is a mob near the zone line you will die before the zone loads, I got triple hit for 200 just so you know... Hope this helps Happy Hunting =)<br>&nbsp;<br>Xianon Nukesforyou <br></td></tr>
