	   <tr><td colspan=2>Marus Seru would be a great place for&nbsp;&nbsp;you two.   At 25 I would hunt by the Netherbian Lair  or Mons Letalis zone line.   If you can pick up a healer that would be great.  As you both hit 30ish,  you could move over to the Santus Seru zone line (tend to get some higher levels, and less crowded) or even try DS near the NL zoneline.<br><br>The mobs tend to roam near the center of the zone (although a few wander to the edges), so the SK can pull a couple of mobs, you can snare, root and blast away while he tanks.<br>&nbsp;<br>imakegood&nbsp;&nbsp;52nd Level Pally.  <br>Ialsomake    52nd Level Wizzy<br>Imakepets    21st Level Necro<br>Readyaim      17th LVL Ranger<br>Bristlebane Server. </td></tr>
